OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,8,Fsaid there is "plenty of stock of
OL,9,Fvaccine supply in the country", as he
OL,10,Fseeks to reassure the public amid an
OL,11,F"unprecedented" meningitis outbreak in
OL,12,FKent.
OL,14,FSome pharmacists have warned of
OL,15,Fshortages of vaccines, with high
OL,16,Fstreet pharmacy Boots implementing a
OL,17,Fqueuing system for customers to enter
OL,18,Fthe vaccination service page of its
OL,19,Fwebsite, with a warning that demand
OL,20,Ffor its MenB jab is currently high.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FSuperdrug has also created a waiting
OL,8,Flist for the vaccine, with a note on
OL,9,Fits website informing customers of a
OL,10,F"national shortage". It said it is
OL,11,F"working with suppliers to access
OL,12,Ffurther stock".
OL,14,FStreeting appeared on ITV's Good
OL,15,FMorning Britain on Wednesday as the UK
OL,16,FHeath Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,17,Fconfirmed there are now 20 cases of
OL,18,Fmeningitis being investigated in Kent.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@SO]sD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FNine of those cases have been
OL,8,Fconfirmed, of which six are the
OL,9,Fmeningitis B strain, known as MenB.
OL,10,FTwo students have died after
OL,11,Fcontracting the bacterial infection.
OL,13,FThe health secretary told Ed Balls and
OL,14,FSusanna Reid that there is "plenty of
OL,15,Fstock of vaccine supply in the
OL,16,Fcountry", although the government are
OL,17,Fnot currently advising those elsewhere
OL,18,Fin the UK to pay for private
OL,19,Fvaccinations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FOlivier Picard, chairman of the
OL,8,FNational Pharmacy Association (NPA),
OL,9,Ftold BBC Radio 4's Today programme
OL,10,Fthere was currently no stock of
OL,11,Fmeningitis B vaccines for people to
OL,12,Fpay for privately.
OL,14,FHe said pharmacies were used to
OL,15,F"bridging the gap between what the NHS
OL,16,Foffers and what patients want".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, that supply has run
OL,8,Fout, and most of our distributors,
OL,9,Fwholesalers have no stock. And whilst
OL,10,Fwe're hearing that there may be some
OL,11,Fstock in the system, it is taking its
OL,12,Ftime to come into our fridges. There's
OL,13,Fno date of resupply," he said.
OL,15,FBut speaking about the issue on GMB,
OL,16,FStreeting said: "On any product line,
OL,17,Fin any pharmacy or shop, they keep
OL,18,Fstocks based on usual patterns of
OL,19,Fdemand. It's not surprising that in
OL,20,Frecent days demand is higher than it
OL,21,Fwould be."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FWhen asked if it was just temporary,
OL,8,FStreeting added: "Yes, in terms of the
OL,9,Funderlying supply, there is plenty
OL,10,Favailable. That is the one thing I'm
OL,11,Fnot worried about."
OL,13,FFrom Wednesday, 5,000 students in
OL,14,Fhalls at Kent University will be able
OL,15,Fto access MenB vaccines in a targeted
OL,16,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FOn the prospect of a wider, national
OL,8,FNHS vaccine roll-out, Streeting said:
OL,9,F"We are going to approach that in an
OL,10,Fevidence-based way, I don't want to do
OL,11,Fthat in a knee-jerk way."
OL,13,FStreeting said that the government are
OL,14,Fcurrently seeking advice from the
OL,15,FJCVI, an independent body of
OL,16,Fscientists who make recommendations to
OL,17,Fgovernment, to look at what has
OL,18,Fhappened in Canterbury and issue fresh
OL,19,Fadvice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
