PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThis could involve making the MenB
OL,13,Fvaccine more widely available through
OL,14,Fthe NHS, something that GMB guest
OL,15,FMichael Rosen called for earlier in
OL,16,Fthe programme.
OL,18,FThe author and poet lost his son,
OL,19,FEddie, 26 years ago. He urged the
OL,20,Fgovernment to "have a look again" at
OL,21,Fgiving people MenB vaccines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,F"If it's less effective, it doesn't
OL,8,Fmean it's not effective if you're
OL,9,Fgiving people the vaccine now," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe majority of young people born
OL,13,Fbefore 2015 are not protected against
OL,14,Fmeningitis B unless they have had the
OL,15,Fjab privately. It was introduced on
OL,16,Fthe NHS for babies in 2015.
OL,18,FAnyone can get meningitis, but it is
OL,19,Fmost commonly caught by babies, young
OL,20,Fchildren, teenagers and young adults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773907468
OL,3,C'Plenty' of meningitis jabs says
OL,4,CStreeting as pharmacies warn of UK
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FUnlike flu and colds, meningitis is
OL,8,Fspread through close personal contact,
OL,9,Fsuch as kissing or sharing drinks and
OL,10,Fvapes.
OL,12,FFollowing the recent outbreak, GPs
OL,13,Facross the country have now been told
OL,14,Fto prescribe antibiotics to anyone who
OL,15,Fvisited a nightclub in Canterbury from
OL,16,FMarch 5-7, plus students from the
OL,17,FUniversity of Kent.
OL,19,FOver 2,500 doses of antibiotics have
OL,20,Falready been given out to students,
OL,21,Fwhich are over 90% effective.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
